  {label: 'Writings', path: '/home'},
  {label: 'Opinions', path: '/home/opinions'},
]

// Card object with SVG icons for interactive elements
cardIcons = [
  { likeAction, className, action, countLike },  // Like button
  { label (comment SVG), className, commentAction, countComments },  // Comment
  { checkBookmark, className, bookmarkAction, countBookmarks },  // Bookmark
  { iconCount, iconView }  // Views counter
]
```

**Card Anatomy**:
1. Banner image (lazy-loaded, clickable)
2. Card content section (title + preview text)
3. Icon bar (user info + interactive buttons)
4. Reading time pill (auto-calculated)
5. Settings menu (3-dot dropdown)

**Interactive Features**:
- Debounced like/bookmark actions (300ms, 100ms respectively)
- View tracking mutation on content click
