3. Promise.allSettled for simultaneous journal + image deletion
4. Success message appears with fade-out animation
5. Query invalidation and timeout reset (1.5s)

### VisitedProfilePostCards.jsx (View Other Users' Posts)
**Differences from ProfilePostCards**:
